org.azeckoski.reflectutils
Class ClassData<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.azeckoski.reflectutils.ClassData<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the class type A class which retrieves and holds all the reflected class data related to a class (annotations, constructors, fields, methods), this is immutable
WARNING: this is NOT cheap and the results need to be cached badly, you should get this from the ClassDataCacher rather than constructing it yourself
public class ClassData<T>
extends Object
